# MERN Chat Application

## ğŸ“Œ Overview
The **MERN Chat Application** is a real-time messaging platform built using the **MERN stack** (MongoDB, Express.js, React, and Node.js). It supports **one-on-one and group chat**, user authentication, and multimedia sharing.

## ğŸš€ Features
- **User Authentication** (Sign Up, Login, JWT-based Authentication)
- **Real-time Messaging** using Socket.io
- **One-on-One & Group Chat Support**
- **Media Uploads** (Images, Files using Cloudinary)
- **Online/Offline Status Indication**
- **Responsive UI** built with React and TailwindCSS
- **MongoDB Atlas for Database**

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
### **Frontend:**
- React.js
- Tailwind CSS
- Zustand for state management
- Axios for API requests

### **Backend:**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB Atlas
- Socket.io for real-time communication
- Cloudinary for media storage
- JWT Authentication

