## ğŸ”§ Setup Instructions
### **1. Clone the Repository**
```sh
git clone https://github.com/bhargavreddi7889/Mern-Chat_application.git
cd Mern-Chat_application
```

### **2. Backend Setup**
```sh
cd backend
npm install  # Install dependencies
cp .env.example .env  # Create .env file and configure it
node src/server.js  # Start the server
```

### **3. Frontend Setup**
```sh
cd ../frontend
npm install  # Install dependencies
npm run dev  # Start the frontend
```

### **4. Running the Application**
- Open **http://localhost:3000/** in your browser to access the chat application.
- Backend runs on **http://localhost:5000/** by default.

## âš¡ API Endpoints
| Endpoint             | Method | Description             |
|---------------------|--------|-------------------------|
| `/api/auth/register` | POST   | User Registration       |
| `/api/auth/login`    | POST   | User Login             |
| `/api/users`        | GET    | Get all users          |
| `/api/messages`     | POST   | Send message           |
| `/api/groups`       | POST   | Create Group Chat      |

